OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start across Lothian
OL,6,Fand Borders with a little drizzle.
OL,7,FBrightening up by afternoon with some
OL,8,Fspells of sunshine, but some cloud
OL,9,Flingering along the east coast.
OL,10,FDumfries and Galloway dry, sunny and
OL,11,Fquite warm.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry.
OL,14,FRemaining dry overnight but clouding
OL,15,Fover across Lothians and Borders.
OL,16,FDumfries and Galloway will be clear
OL,17,Fwith some patchy frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
