OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FOvernight low cloud mostly
OL,6,Fburning off in the east, but may
OL,7,Flinger along parts of the east coast.
OL,8,FOtherwise dry and sunny. Becoming
OL,9,Fwarm, but cooler along the east coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FRemaining
OL,12,Fdry and settled into the weekend with
OL,13,Fplenty of sunshine. Low cloud may be
OL,14,Fslow to clear eastern coastal
OL,15,Fdistricts. Warm inland, but cooler
OL,16,Fnear the east coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
